<span id="SENTENCE_51">cortége</span>
</i>
<span id="SENTENCE_52">.</span>
<span id="SENTENCE_53">They waited, but no throat-cutting that morning; no august spectacle of satisfied justice; and the eager spectators were obliged to return, disappointed of the expected breakfast of blood.</span>
