</a>
<span id="SENTENCE_285">Square where his imaginary Sedleys lived—a curious proof of the reality his creations had for his mind.'</span>
<span id="SENTENCE_286">The same writer tells us that when he congratulated Thackeray, many years ago, on the touch in 'Vanity Fair' in which Becky admires her husband when he is giving Lord Steyne the chastisement which ruins</span>
<i>
<span id="SENTENCE_287">her</span>
